Membership
Return to Clubhouse & Lifestyle
We understand a great golf experience is as much about the people as it is the course design and conditioning. Whether a Resident or Invitational member, the Astor Creek golf membership experience is grounded in hospitality with a goal to create camaraderie. Beyond great play, a full-time Lifestyle Coordinator is focused on planning and executing social events, activities and programs that create connection between members and fun for all.
For Astor Creek new home buyers, club membership is included.
Resident Membership
• Unlimited Family Golf Privileges as outlined in Rules & Regulations
• Unlimited Driving Range, Short Game Complex and Practice Green access
• 14-day Advanced Tee Time Booking
• Unlimited access to all Clubhouse amenities including Fitness Center, Pool, Dining, Pickleball, Tennis and Sports Courts
•
Membership INCLUDED with the Purchase of a New Home
Invitational Membership
• Unlimited Family Golf Privileges as outlined in Rules & Regulations
• Unlimited Driving Range, Short Game Complex and Practice Green access
• 10-day Advanced Tee Time Booking
• Clubhouse Dining
• Membership requires an initial Club Contribution and Annual Dues -
click here
to contact the Astor Creek Director of Golf for details

Kolter Homes | New Home Builder | Florida | Georgia | North Carolina | South Carolina
New Homes
Built Around You
in Florida, Georgia and the Carolinas
We understand that buying and building a new home is one of the biggest decisions you can make. More than just a house, you are searching for community, and a lifestyle that best suits you, your family and friends. You should be able to make clear decisions based on your priorities. That's why Kolter Homes has developed a simple recipe that has helped thousands of new home shoppers find the right community, build their ideal home and enjoy life in Florida, Georgia and the Carolinas.
Kolter’s
Cresswind
55+ communities across the Southeast offer active adults new homes and activities designed for the way they live today and into the future. This award-winning concept empowers Cresswind residents to
"Set Yourself
F

E
"
based on the cornerstones of
Fitness,

and

It is the recipe
to

and includes a wide variety of programs and facilities such as fitness classes, pickleball, social clubs, concerts, guest speakers, and art studios at resident-exclusive clubhouses. To keep residents' calendars fresh, fun and full, Kolter has a
Director of Lifestyle
who oversees the programs, events and activities so you can savor the good stuff.
This happier, healthier mindset also extends to the design of your new home.
KOLTER
HOMES Design Galleries offers hundreds of choices to personalize your new home to best fit your lifestyle. You'll enjoy a wide variety of floorplan layouts and structural options. Helping you along the way to make clear decisions such as selecting colors, cabinets, flooring and fixtures is
KOLTER
HOMES' team of design professionals. And by using innovative, energy-efficient construction techniques, materials, products and standards,
KOLTER
HOMES ensures lasting value and a healthier home for you and your family.
Kolter Homes, founded as
Kolter Signature Homes LLC,
is an affiliate of
The Kolter Group LLC.
The Kolter Group LLC, together with its affiliates, is a private investment firm focused on real estate development, investment and construction. The Kolter Group LLC, together with its affiliates, has invested in projects with expected value in excess of $30 billion of real estate transactions (both realized and in-process) across multiple asset classes and geographies.
